modules.description: Handles geometric transformations including rotation, scaling, and translation of 2D vectors using float-based coordinates. Processes lists of points and line segments to generate modified shapes for rendering. Used in game development to animate object movements and adjust visual layouts dynamically.

Converts Common Mark strings to HTML using a strict or lenient parsing mode. Processes tuples containing document metadata and content, applying conversion only to the content portion. Enables seamless integration of marked-up text into HTML output pipelines.
